WEBVTT

33:06.770 --> 33:08.090 line:80%
now that I have met you—

33:08.180 --> 33:09.910 line:80%
how could my heart not rejoice?

33:10.460 --> 33:11.570 line:80%
The meaning of this poem line is that

33:11.570 --> 33:14.470 line:80%
amidst the gloom and pouring rain,

33:14.570 --> 33:16.140 line:80%
the roosters crow in panic.
